						<h3><b>Benefits of Buying Fair Trade</b></h3>

						<p>Buying Fair Trade food and goods brings benefits for both producers and consumers alike. For producers it means a better standard of living, and for children in affected regions it means an end to child labor. Fair Trade also helps workers receive higher wages for their work, and it proscribes slavery. Consumers also benefit because Fair Trade goods are of a better quality and Fair Trade food is free of harmful chemicals such as pesticides.</p>
