						<h3><b>How to Find Fair Trade Items</b></h3>

						<p>Finding Fair Trade foods and crafted goods has become much easier with the arrival and evolution of the Internet. Many grocery store chains offer Fair Trade sections within their stores, and merchants dedicated to Fair Trade goods can be found online. When shopping online or at a store, finding Fair Trade products is as simple as looking for goods bearing Fair Trade labels. The Fair Trade Resource Network is one resource that offers information on which labels to look for.</p>
